data.description: Gorgeous Brices Crossing home! Four bedroom, 3 full bath. Kitchen has stainless appliances (Refrigerator, dishwasher & stove purchased in 2022, microwave 2021). Cathedral ceiling in the living room with gas log fire place. Dining room also has cathedral ceiling and chair rail molding. Brand new carpet in 2 bedrooms. Screened porch and fenced backyard for privacy. 2 car garage. Corner lot. Seller offering $2000 concession with acceptable offer. Award winning Creekside Elementary district. Short distance to Downtown New Bern and our beautiful Crystal Coast beaches!
